data.description: Looking for a newly updated home nestled on a cul-de-sac in sought after Stillwater Canyon? This spacious home offers an open floor plan ideal for entertaining & hosting events. The chefs kitchen offers a gas cooktop, butlers pantry and updated granite counter tops to go with your fresh white cabinets. Don’t miss the private backyard that offers a fenced-off half sized basketball court perfect for the basketball athlete! Enjoy a morning coffee on the 2nd floor balcony that welcomes you to the family room that could also be used as a training space. Want to watch a movie? This home features a media room on the second floor that comes with a projector, screen and sound system... Just bring your snacks!
